see http://texdoc.net/texmf-dist/doc/latex/beamer/doc/beameruserguide.pdf for
more info on beamer theming

This incorporates the official VT [brand colors](https://vt.edu/brand.html)
into a theme.

Works mostly with outer themes of smoothbars, miniframes, and tree. others are
not as nice for what is specified in beamercolorthemeHokieLayout.sty
